title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 52-8.2 - Licensure
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 52-8.2 - Licensure

State Regulations

Reproductive tissue banks, insemination/implantation sites and semen processing facilities shall not operate unless licensed as tissue banks pursuant to Subpart 52-2 of this Part. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10

52-8.2
